1.06 2025-07-10T05:45:57Z

    - add --yankees to autoload list
    - set HOME for test environment
    - update i18n module to use LC_TIME environment variable
      - Add env=LC_TIME parameter to i18n::setopt configuration
      - Update documentation to reflect LC_TIME usage instead of LANG
      - Changes affect --i18n and --i18n-v options behavior

